## Objectives
- Rapid triage, containment, eradication, and recovery.
- Communication to stakeholders and regulators when required.

## Roles & Responsibilities
- **Incident Commander:** Security Lead (or delegate)
- **Scribe:** Assigned by IC
- **Comms:** IC coordinates with Legal and Exec team

## SLAs
- Triage P1 incidents within 15 minutes.
- Notify impacted customers within 72 hours, if applicable.

## Post-Incident
- Root cause analysis within 5 business days.
- Action items tracked to closure in the ticketing system.